<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="22May1933"><font color="red">22 May 1933</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): Mr Joyce asked me to send you for safe keeping the receipt I received for Mr Morley of Messrs Faber and Faber for the corrected episodes of <i>Work in Progress</i> that I delivered up to him in March. </div>
